David Shadle
[[Image:Oh Noz!.jpg|thumb|left|100px|Watch out for that knife!]]{{Killers}}
'''David Shadle''' is a 21 year old [[cock]]juggler from Slickville, PA. He enjoys the American Pie  series, killing his girlfriend, and the music of Nirvana and [[Metallica]]. On March 1st 2006 he was charged with first-degree murder and criminal homicide in the death of his girlfriend Jessica.
== Details ==
Jessica was found dead at 4:30 PM on February 28th by some guy who apparently has no name. She was last seen alive with this [[cock]]mongrel of a boyfriend at 10:30 PM the previous day.

[[police|State police]] charged Shadle with criminal homicide and first-degree [[pwning]], as well as receiving stolen property. They said they received a tip from some [[hobo]] who saw Shadle in a car with another person.

Shadle is currently enrolled in the Accelerated Rehabilitative Dipshit program for shitheads in Westermoreland County.

